1
00:00:23,190 --> 00:00:25,192
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

2
00:00:46,463 --> 00:00:50,634
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG ROAD ♪

3
00:00:50,676 --> 00:00:54,013
♪ GETTING FROM THERE TO HERE ♪

4
00:00:54,054 --> 00:00:57,975
♪ IT'S BEEN A LONG TIME ♪

5
00:00:58,017 --> 00:01:02,021
♪ BUT MY TIME IS FINALLY NEAR ♪

6
00:01:02,062 --> 00:01:06,233
♪ AND I WILL SEE MY DREAM
COME ALIVE AT LAST ♪

7
00:01:06,274 --> 00:01:09,778
♪ I WILL TOUCH THE SKY ♪

8
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,532
♪ AND THEY'RE NOT GONNA
HOLD ME DOWN NO MORE ♪

9
00:01:13,574 --> 00:01:16,827
♪ NO, THEY'RE NOT GONNA
CHANGE MY MIND ♪

10
00:01:16,869 --> 00:01:19,454
♪ 'CAUSE I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

11
00:01:19,496 --> 00:01:21,749
♪ OF THE HEART ♪

12
00:01:21,790 --> 00:01:24,626
♪ I'M GOING WHERE MY HEART
WILL TAKE ME ♪

13
00:01:24,668 --> 00:01:29,631
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH TO BELIEVE ♪

14
00:01:29,673 --> 00:01:32,384
♪ I CAN DO ANYTHING ♪

15
00:01:32,426 --> 00:01:37,264
♪ I'VE GOT STRENGTH
OF THE SOUL ♪

16
00:01:37,305 --> 00:01:40,183
♪ AND NO ONE'S GONNA BEND
OR BREAK ME ♪

17
00:01:40,225 --> 00:01:45,773
♪ I CAN REACH ANY STAR ♪

18
00:01:45,814 --> 00:01:47,066
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

19
00:01:47,106 --> 00:01:49,985
♪ I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT, I'VE GOT ♪

20
00:01:50,027 --> 00:01:53,655
♪ I'VE GOT FAITH ♪

21
00:01:53,697 --> 00:01:57,409
♪ FAITH OF THE HEART ♪

22
00:02:12,841 --> 00:02:14,426
TUCKER: MAYBE IT'S JUST ME,
BUT IT SEEMS LIKE

23
00:02:14,468 --> 00:02:17,679
THESE VULCAN STARCHARTS
TAKE ALL THE FUN OUT OF IT.

24
00:02:17,721 --> 00:02:19,473
WE'RE SUPPOSED TO BE EXPLORERS,
AREN'T WE?

25
00:02:19,514 --> 00:02:20,766
ARCHER: THAT'S
THE GENERAL IDEA.

26
00:02:20,808 --> 00:02:22,017
TUCKER: WHERE'S THE EXPLORATION

27
00:02:22,059 --> 00:02:24,436
IN GOING PLACES
PEOPLE HAVE ALREADY BEEN?

28
00:02:24,478 --> 00:02:25,854
ARCHER: WELL, FOR ONE THING,

29
00:02:25,896 --> 00:02:27,856
WE'VE NEVER BEEN
TO THESE PLACES.

30
00:02:27,898 --> 00:02:29,858
FOR ANOTHER,

31
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:32,569
REMEMBER THAT PROTOSTAR
WE RAN ACROSS LAST WEEK?

32
00:02:32,611 --> 00:02:33,946
TUCKER: YEAH.

33
00:02:33,988 --> 00:02:35,155
ARCHER: I'M NOT SEEING IT HERE.

34
00:02:37,741 --> 00:02:39,118
TUCKER: ARE YOU SAYING

35
00:02:39,159 --> 00:02:41,912
THOSE VULCAN STARCHARTS
AREN'T ALL THAT ACCURATE?

36
00:02:44,581 --> 00:02:46,750
WELL, IF THAT'S TRUE, GOOD LUCK
GETTING THEM TO ADMIT IT.

37
00:02:46,792 --> 00:02:48,251
[ ARCHER LAUGHING ]

38
00:02:48,293 --> 00:02:49,210
[ DOOR CHIMES ]

39
00:02:49,252 --> 00:02:50,253
COME IN.

40
00:02:52,965 --> 00:02:54,382
YOU WANTED
TO SEE ME, CAPTAIN?

41
00:02:54,424 --> 00:02:56,051
ARCHER: AS A MATTER OF FACT,
MR. TUCKER AND I

42
00:02:56,093 --> 00:02:58,012
WERE LOOKING
AT THESE STARCHARTS.

43
00:02:58,053 --> 00:02:59,763
THERE'S A PLANET
A FEW LIGHT-YEARS OFF

44
00:02:59,805 --> 00:03:01,640
OUR CURRENT HEADING.

45
00:03:01,682 --> 00:03:03,017
I'M FAMILIAR WITH IT.

46
00:03:03,058 --> 00:03:04,559
ARCHER: WELL,
THE DATA INDICATES

47
00:03:04,601 --> 00:03:07,228
THERE'S A REMOTE OUTPOST
RIGHT HERE

48
00:03:07,270 --> 00:03:08,355
ON THE NORTHERN HEMISPHERE.

49
00:03:09,982 --> 00:03:11,608
P'JEM.

50
00:03:11,650 --> 00:03:15,320
ARCHER: I TAKE IT THIS P'JEM
IS UNDER VULCAN JURISDICTION?

51
00:03:15,362 --> 00:03:17,405
IT'S AN ANCIENT
SPIRITUAL RETREAT,

52
00:03:17,447 --> 00:03:21,451
A REMOTE SANCTUARY FOR KOLINAHR
AND PEACEFUL MEDITATION.

53
00:03:21,493 --> 00:03:22,828
TUCKER: KOLINAHR?

54
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:26,123
THE VULCAN PURGING OF EMOTION.

55
00:03:26,165 --> 00:03:27,332
ARCHER: WELL, THAT
SOUNDS INTERESTING.

56
00:03:29,250 --> 00:03:31,170
HOW DO YOU THINK THEY'D
FEEL ABOUT A VISIT?

57
00:03:31,210 --> 00:03:33,922
P'JEM IS A PLACE OF
QUIET CONTEMPLATION, CAPTAIN.

58
00:03:33,964 --> 00:03:36,050
I'M NOT CERTAIN
WE'D BE WELCOME.

59
00:03:36,091 --> 00:03:38,593
TUCKER: IT'S BECAUSE VULCANS
THINK WE SMELL BAD, ISN'T IT?

60
00:03:41,013 --> 00:03:42,806
ARCHER: IT'S NOT EVERY DAY
WE GET A CHANCE

61
00:03:42,848 --> 00:03:45,767
TO SEE AN ANCIENT
VULCAN MONASTERY.

62
00:03:45,809 --> 00:03:49,021
I'D SAY A STOPOVER IS
TOO GOOD TO PASS UP...

63
00:03:49,063 --> 00:03:51,065
UNLESS YOU DISAGREE.

64
00:03:51,106 --> 00:03:53,650
I'LL RESEARCH
THE PROPER PROTOCOLS.

65
00:03:53,692 --> 00:03:56,153
ARCHER: GOOD. ARCHER TO HELM.

66
00:03:56,195 --> 00:03:57,612
TRAVIS: GO AHEAD, SIR.

67
00:03:57,654 --> 00:03:59,489
ARCHER: PREPARE TO LAY IN
A COURSE CORRECTION.

68
00:03:59,531 --> 00:04:01,200
T'POL WILL GIVE YOU
THE COORDINATES.

69
00:04:01,241 --> 00:04:02,242
TRAVIS: UNDERSTOOD.

70
00:04:09,666 --> 00:04:10,625
WELL, YOU MUST
BE LOOKING FORWARD

71
00:04:10,667 --> 00:04:12,711
TO VISITING THE SANCTUARY.

72
00:04:12,753 --> 00:04:14,755
IT WAS THE CAPTAIN'S IDEA.

73
00:04:14,796 --> 00:04:15,839
PHLOX: BUT SUCH AN OPPORTUNITY

74
00:04:15,881 --> 00:04:18,258
TO APPRECIATE
YOUR CULTURAL HISTORY.

75
00:04:18,299 --> 00:04:20,635
IT IS A VULCAN SANCTUARY,
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU MEAN.

76
00:04:20,677 --> 00:04:22,096
PHLOX: PRECISELY MY POINT.

77
00:04:22,137 --> 00:04:24,056
YOU'LL BE ABLE TO INTRODUCE
SOME OF YOUR OWN PEOPLE

78
00:04:24,098 --> 00:04:25,265
TO YOUR NEW CREW.

79
00:04:27,768 --> 00:04:31,230
OH. I BELIEVE I SEE
THE SOURCE OF YOUR MISGIVINGS.

80
00:04:31,271 --> 00:04:34,191
BEING SEEN WITH A HUMAN CREW.

81
00:04:34,233 --> 00:04:36,568
T'POL: IT COULD CREATE
A CERTAIN AWKWARDNESS.

82
00:04:43,242 --> 00:04:46,453
MAY I? HMM.

83
00:04:48,247 --> 00:04:50,373
MMM.

84
00:04:50,415 --> 00:04:54,669
I CONFESS, I FEEL AWKWARD MYSELF
ON THIS SHIP SOMETIMES,

85
00:04:54,711 --> 00:04:55,837
OUT OF PLACE.

86
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:57,297
BUT WHAT IS THAT VULCAN MOTTO?

87
00:04:57,338 --> 00:04:59,716
UM, INFINITE DIVERSITY--

88
00:04:59,758 --> 00:05:01,426
IN INFINITE COMBINATIONS.

89
00:05:01,468 --> 00:05:05,222
MM! [ CHUCKLES ]
AND WHAT IS DIVERSITY

90
00:05:05,264 --> 00:05:07,515
BUT A CELEBRATION
OF DIFFERENCES?

91
00:05:12,271 --> 00:05:16,108
I WONDER IF YOU MIGHT REMIND ME
OF OUR MISSION ON THIS VESSEL?

92
00:05:16,150 --> 00:05:19,069
PLEASE, INDULGE ME.
[ CHUCKLES ]

93
00:05:19,111 --> 00:05:20,988
OUR MISSION IS
TO MAKE CONTACT

94
00:05:21,029 --> 00:05:22,656
WITH THOSE
WHO HUMANS CONSIDER

95
00:05:22,697 --> 00:05:25,408
NEW LIFE
AND NEW CIVILIZATIONS.

96
00:05:25,450 --> 00:05:28,703
IN OTHER WORDS,
TO SEEK INFINITE DIVERSITY.

97
00:05:28,745 --> 00:05:30,080
I SUPPOSE SO.

98
00:05:30,122 --> 00:05:32,373
WELL, THEN, IT SEEMS TO ME
A CULTURAL EXCHANGE

99
00:05:32,415 --> 00:05:34,459
BETWEEN YOUR VULCAN BRETHREN
AND YOUR HUMAN CREW

100
00:05:34,501 --> 00:05:37,545
IS SIMPLY A FURTHERANCE
OF THAT MISSION.

101
00:05:37,587 --> 00:05:38,546
[ CHUCKLES ]

102
00:05:53,770 --> 00:05:55,730
TUCKER: THEY DON'T EVEN KNOW
WE'RE COMING?

103
00:05:55,772 --> 00:05:57,356
T'POL: IT WASN'T POSSIBLE
TO HAIL THEM.

104
00:05:57,398 --> 00:05:59,609
THE MONKS CONSIDER
TECHNOLOGY A DISTRACTION

105
00:05:59,651 --> 00:06:01,486
FROM THEIR
SPIRITUAL PURSUITS.

106
00:06:01,528 --> 00:06:03,905
ARCHER: I DON'T LIKE DROPPING IN
ON PEOPLE UNANNOUNCED.

107
00:06:03,947 --> 00:06:08,243
IT WON'T BE A PROBLEM AS LONG AS
WE OBSERVE THE PROPER PROTOCOLS.

108
00:06:08,285 --> 00:06:11,997
WHEN WE ARRIVE, WE'LL BE GREETED
BY A VULCAN ELDER.

109
00:06:12,039 --> 00:06:13,957
YOU SHOULD NOT SPEAK TO HIM

110
00:06:13,999 --> 00:06:17,044
OR ANY MEMBER OF THE ORDER
UNLESS SPOKEN TO FIRST.

111
00:06:17,085 --> 00:06:18,962
IF THEY APPEAR
TO BE MEDITATING,

112
00:06:19,004 --> 00:06:22,465
DO NOT APPROACH THEM
OR ATTEMPT TO MAKE CONVERSATION.

113
00:06:22,507 --> 00:06:26,469
ALSO, MAINTAIN QUIET
AT ALL TIMES,

114
00:06:26,511 --> 00:06:28,847
AND DO NOT TOUCH OR DISTURB

115
00:06:28,889 --> 00:06:32,142
ANY ARTIFACTS, RELICS,
OR ORNAMENTATION.

116
00:06:32,184 --> 00:06:34,978
IF WE ARRIVE AT THEIR TIME
OF COMMUNAL KOLINAHR,

117
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:37,605
IT'S LIKELY WE'LL
BE TURNED AWAY.

118
00:06:37,647 --> 00:06:39,024
AT THE CONCLUSION
OF OUR VISIT,

119
00:06:39,066 --> 00:06:40,817
WE'LL BE OFFERED
THE STONE OF J'KAH

120
00:06:40,859 --> 00:06:42,944
AS A GESTURE OF SALUTATION.

121
00:06:42,986 --> 00:06:44,321
ACCEPT IT.

122
00:06:44,363 --> 00:06:45,906
THEN BOW SLIGHTLY,

123
00:06:45,947 --> 00:06:49,492
AND OBSERVE A RESPECTFUL SILENCE
FOR APPROXIMATELY 5 SECONDS.

124
00:06:56,917 --> 00:06:58,459
TUCKER: I THOUGHT STARFLEET
TRAINING WAS TOUGH.

125
00:07:08,511 --> 00:07:11,306
TUCKER: YOU SAY THIS IS A PLACE
TO PURGE EMOTIONS?

126
00:07:11,348 --> 00:07:13,474
LOOKS LIKE SOMEBODY HAD
TO PURGE PRETTY BAD.

127
00:07:13,516 --> 00:07:15,518
HE BASHED THE DOOR IN.

128
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,605
T'POL: THE TEMPLE IS ALMOST
3,000 YEARS OLD, COMMANDER.

129
00:07:18,646 --> 00:07:20,648
YOU CAN'T EXPECT IT TO BE
IN PRISTINE CONDITION.

130
00:07:22,692 --> 00:07:24,694
[ BELL CLANGS ]

131
00:08:06,694 --> 00:08:08,738
[T'POL AND MAN WHISPERING]

132
00:08:21,001 --> 00:08:24,254
T'POL: HE SAYS WE HAVE ARRIVED
AT THE TIME OF KOLINAHR.

133
00:08:24,296 --> 00:08:26,298
THE ORDER MUST REMAIN
IN SILENT REFLECTION

134
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:28,008
THROUGHOUT THE LUNAR CYCLE.

135
00:08:28,049 --> 00:08:30,260
THEY ARE NOT TO BE DISTURBED.

136
00:08:30,302 --> 00:08:31,845
ARCHER: OH, THAT'S TOO BAD.

137
00:08:31,886 --> 00:08:34,848
WELL, AT LEAST WE GOT
TO SEE THE PLACE.

138
00:08:39,602 --> 00:08:41,688
T'POL: YOUR SERVICE HONORS US.

139
00:08:41,729 --> 00:08:43,398
BEFORE WE LEAVE,
MAY I REQUEST

140
00:08:43,440 --> 00:08:47,444
THE OFFERING OF THE J'KAH STONE
FOR MY DISTINGUISHED GUESTS?

141
00:08:47,486 --> 00:08:48,611
MAN: PLEASE WAIT.

142
00:09:01,082 --> 00:09:02,334
ARCHER: IS SOMETHING WRONG?

143
00:09:04,085 --> 00:09:05,879
T'POL: IT'S PROBABLY NOTHING.

144
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,047
ARCHER: BUT?

145
00:09:09,216 --> 00:09:10,884
T'POL: THIS IS THE MAIN ATRIUM.

146
00:09:10,925 --> 00:09:13,220
THERE SHOULD BE MORE THAN ONE
MEMBER OF THE ORDER PRESENT.

147
00:09:15,596 --> 00:09:17,516
AND THE ICON IN THAT SHRINE
IS PERCHED

148
00:09:17,557 --> 00:09:20,310
AT AN ODD ANGLE.

149
00:09:20,352 --> 00:09:22,479
TUCKER: ODDLY PERCHED, HUH?

150
00:09:22,521 --> 00:09:24,772
WE'D BETTER CALL
STARFLEET COMMAND.

151
00:09:24,814 --> 00:09:27,317
T'POL: THAT'S NOT ALL, CAPTAIN.

152
00:09:27,359 --> 00:09:31,821
THE VULCAN ELDER SEEMS...
AGITATED.

153
00:09:31,863 --> 00:09:33,031
TUCKER: YOU CALL THAT AGITATED?

154
00:09:36,659 --> 00:09:40,038
ARCHER: YOU KNOW, I THINK
THE OLDEST MONASTERY

155
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:44,543
I EVER VISITED
WAS IN NGARI, TIBET,

156
00:09:44,584 --> 00:09:50,757
BUT IT WASN'T NEARLY
AS BIG AS THIS PLACE.

157
00:09:50,798 --> 00:09:54,511
I'VE HEARD IT CAN TAKE DAYS
TO EXPLORE THIS SITE.

158
00:09:54,553 --> 00:09:57,097
IT'D TAKE AT LEAST THAT LONG
TO CLEAN THE PLACE UP.

159
00:09:57,138 --> 00:09:58,765
FORGIVE THE DISARRAY.

160
00:09:58,806 --> 00:10:00,725
KOLINAHR ENCOURAGES
MEMBERS OF OUR ORDER

161
00:10:00,767 --> 00:10:03,186
TO FACE
THEIR VESTIGIAL EMOTIONS.

162
00:10:03,228 --> 00:10:05,272
THE REPERCUSSIONS CAN
SOMETIMES BE VIOLENT.

163
00:10:07,732 --> 00:10:10,068
ELDER: PLEASE.

164
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,986
THIS IS THE STONE OF J'KAH,

165
00:10:12,028 --> 00:10:14,531
WHICH REPRESENTS THE FOUNDATION
OF ALL WE BELIEVE--

166
00:10:14,573 --> 00:10:16,783
A LIFE OF ORDER AND CONTROL
THROUGH LOGIC.

167
00:10:20,328 --> 00:10:22,372
[ SPEAKING VULCAN ]

168
00:10:30,213 --> 00:10:33,425
ARCHER: WHAT'S ALL THAT
MEAN, ANYWAY?

169
00:10:33,467 --> 00:10:36,553
IT IS A TRADITIONAL LITANY,
PASSED DOWN FOR GENERATIONS.

170
00:10:36,595 --> 00:10:38,846
ARCHER: DOES IT MEAN I GET
GOOD LUCK OR SOMETHING?

171
00:10:38,888 --> 00:10:40,265
OH, YOU'RE THINKING
OF THE BLARNEY STONE, CAPTAIN,

172
00:10:40,307 --> 00:10:42,434
OR WHEN YOU PAT
THE BUDDHA'S BELLY.

173
00:10:48,982 --> 00:10:50,066
ARCHER: I GUESS YOU'RE RIGHT.

174
00:10:51,692 --> 00:10:53,653
TOO BAD WE, UH...

175
00:10:53,694 --> 00:10:55,655
DIDN'T BRING A CAMERA,
HUH, COMMANDER?

176
00:10:57,324 --> 00:10:59,409
ELDER: PLEASE,
YOU MUST LEAVE NOW.

177
00:11:01,411 --> 00:11:03,663
TUCKER: YOU EVER BEEN
TO THE SAN FRANCISCO ZOO?

178
00:11:03,704 --> 00:11:04,998
NOW THERE'S SOMETHING
YOU SHOULD SEE.

179
00:11:18,094 --> 00:11:19,471
[ WEAPONS CHARGING ]

180
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,809
ARCHER: FRIENDS OF YOURS?

181
00:11:30,898 --> 00:11:32,400
SOMEHOW I DIDN'T THINK SO.

182
00:11:36,404 --> 00:11:37,405
[ TUCKER SIGHS ]

183
00:11:47,832 --> 00:11:49,334
ALIEN: STOP LOOKING AT ME.

184
00:11:49,376 --> 00:11:51,919
TUCKER: OKAY, OKAY, DON'T GET
YOUR ANTENNAS IN A TWIST.

185
00:12:07,644 --> 00:12:10,063
ALIEN: WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL US
ONE OF YOUR PEOPLE WAS ABOARD?

186
00:12:10,104 --> 00:12:11,981
ELDER: IT'S AN EARTH VESSEL.
I DIDN'T KNOW.

187
00:12:12,023 --> 00:12:15,276
ALIEN 2: WHAT DOES THAT MEAN--
EARTH? WHAT IS THAT?

188
00:12:15,318 --> 00:12:17,736
ARCHER: IT'S WHERE WE'RE FROM.

189
00:12:17,778 --> 00:12:19,447
IT'S OUR HOMEWORLD.

190
00:12:19,489 --> 00:12:21,824
ALIEN: WHY DID YOU COME HERE?

191
00:12:21,866 --> 00:12:23,076
ANSWER ME, PINK-SKIN!

192
00:12:27,163 --> 00:12:30,166
ARCHER: THIS PLANET
WAS ALONG OUR COURSE.

193
00:12:30,208 --> 00:12:32,252
WE ONLY CAME TO VISIT
THE SANCTUARY.

194
00:12:32,293 --> 00:12:34,254
ALIEN: LIAR!

195
00:12:34,295 --> 00:12:37,048
WHAT'S YOUR MISSION?

196
00:12:37,090 --> 00:12:38,633
ARE YOU A SUPPLY SHIP
BRINGING THEM

197
00:12:38,675 --> 00:12:41,261
MORE SURVEILLANCE EQUIPMENT?

198
00:12:41,302 --> 00:12:42,596
ARCHER: WE'RE NOT
BRINGING THEM ANYTHING.

199
00:12:42,637 --> 00:12:43,680
ALIEN 2: YOU BROUGHT HER.

200
00:12:43,722 --> 00:12:45,265
ARCHER: SHE'S MY
SCIENCE OFFICER.

201
00:12:45,306 --> 00:12:47,808
ALIEN: SO YOU ADMIT YOU'RE
WORKING WITH THE VULCANS?

202
00:12:47,850 --> 00:12:50,937
ARCHER: I'LL ADMIT I HAVE
A VULCAN SCIENCE OFFICER

203
00:12:50,978 --> 00:12:52,647
AND THAT I CAME HERE
OUT OF CURIOSITY.

204
00:12:52,689 --> 00:12:55,483
NOW IF YOU DON'T MIND
MY ASKING,

205
00:12:55,525 --> 00:12:56,984
WHAT ARE<i> YOU</i> DOING HERE?

206
00:12:58,777 --> 00:13:00,321
[ ALIEN SCOFFS ]

207
00:13:00,363 --> 00:13:01,281
[ ARCHER GRUNTS ]

208
00:13:01,322 --> 00:13:04,033
TUCKER: HEY!

209
00:13:04,075 --> 00:13:05,744
HE'S TELLING THE TRUTH.

210
00:13:05,784 --> 00:13:08,246
WE CAME FOR A VISIT,
THAT'S ALL.

211
00:13:08,288 --> 00:13:11,207
ALIEN: WE SCANNED YOUR SHIP
IN ORBIT.

212
00:13:11,249 --> 00:13:14,210
YOU'RE VERY WELL ARMED FOR
PEOPLE WHO CAME FOR A VISIT.

213
00:13:17,505 --> 00:13:21,342
YOU...AND THE PINK-SKINS

214
00:13:21,384 --> 00:13:24,596
HAVE PROVEN
WHAT WE ALREADY KNEW.

215
00:13:24,638 --> 00:13:27,515
THIS IS FAR MORE
THAN A SANCTUARY.

216
00:13:33,271 --> 00:13:35,148
[ COUGHS ]

217
00:13:38,526 --> 00:13:41,279
ALIEN 2: I'LL ENJOY HAVING YOU
AS A PRISONER.

218
00:13:49,537 --> 00:13:51,830
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

219
00:13:51,872 --> 00:13:54,000
TUCKER: NOW,<i> THESE</i> GUYS
ARE AGITATED.

220
00:13:54,041 --> 00:13:56,043
[GROANING ]

221
00:14:03,593 --> 00:14:06,471
THEY'RE ANDORIANS, CAPTAIN.

222
00:14:06,513 --> 00:14:09,890
THEY'RE KNOWN FOR THEIR
SUSPICIOUS AND VOLATILE NATURE.

223
00:14:09,932 --> 00:14:10,849
ANDORIANS?

224
00:14:10,891 --> 00:14:12,602
T'POL: YES, SIR.

225
00:14:12,644 --> 00:14:15,854
ELDER: OUR TWO SPECIES ARE
FROM NEIGHBORING SYSTEMS.

226
00:14:15,896 --> 00:14:19,900
WE'VE BEEN IN CONFLICT
FOR MANY YEARS.

227
00:14:19,942 --> 00:14:22,612
T'POL: THEY RESENT
OUR SUPERIOR REASONING

228
00:14:22,654 --> 00:14:24,905
AND OUR TECHNOLOGY.

229
00:14:24,947 --> 00:14:26,907
THEY EVEN BELIEVE
THAT WE INTEND TO MOUNT

230
00:14:26,949 --> 00:14:28,909
AN INVASION
ON THEIR HOMEWORLD.

231
00:14:28,951 --> 00:14:32,413
ELDER: IN ORDER TO
ALLEVIATE TENSIONS,
WE NEGOTIATED A TREATY,

232
00:14:32,455 --> 00:14:36,626
BUT SOME ANDORIAN FACTIONS STILL
BELIEVE WE'RE BENT ON CONQUEST.

233
00:14:36,668 --> 00:14:38,919
WHAT DO THEY WANT
WITH A 3,000-YEAR-OLD TEMPLE?

234
00:14:38,961 --> 00:14:42,173
THEY BELIEVE WE ARE HIDING
A LONG-RANGE SENSOR ARRAY.

235
00:14:44,217 --> 00:14:46,511
THIS IS A PLACE
OF INTROSPECTION, CAPTAIN.

236
00:14:46,553 --> 00:14:50,139
THERE ARE NO SPIES HERE
AND NO TECHNOLOGY.

237
00:14:50,181 --> 00:14:51,432
TUCKER: SO WHAT
ARE YOU GONNA DO,

238
00:14:51,474 --> 00:14:55,228
JUST SIT HERE AND LET THEM
RANSACK THE PLACE?

239
00:14:55,269 --> 00:14:59,190
TYPICALLY, THEY MAKE A GREAT
DISPLAY OF THEIR INDIGNANCE.

240
00:14:59,232 --> 00:15:02,360
WHEN THEY FIND NOTHING,
THEY LEAVE.

241
00:15:02,402 --> 00:15:03,986
THE ANDORIANS WERE HERE
TWICE BEFORE

242
00:15:04,028 --> 00:15:06,656
AND BOTH TIMES LEFT
WITHIN A DAY.

243
00:15:06,698 --> 00:15:11,369
UNFORTUNATELY, YOUR ARRIVAL
HAS AMPLIFIED THEIR SUSPICIONS.

244
00:15:11,411 --> 00:15:12,912
YOU'VE ENDANGERED US ALL.

245
00:15:19,168 --> 00:15:20,920
TUCKER: NO GOOD DEED
GOES UNPUNISHED.

246
00:15:23,798 --> 00:15:25,925
REED: THE SHUTTLE'S SENSORS
SHOULD'VE PICKED IT UP.

247
00:15:25,966 --> 00:15:27,301
HOSHI: THEY WENT
TO VISIT SOME MONKS.

248
00:15:27,343 --> 00:15:28,845
WHY WOULD THEY SCAN
FOR ALIEN SHIPS?

249
00:15:28,887 --> 00:15:31,222
REED: IT SHOULD BE STANDARD
PROCEDURE, THAT'S WHY.

250
00:15:31,264 --> 00:15:33,140
IN ANY EVENT, THERE IT IS.

251
00:15:33,182 --> 00:15:34,100
TRAVIS: THERE WHAT IS?

252
00:15:34,141 --> 00:15:35,602
REED: A VESSEL, NOT VULCAN.

253
00:15:35,643 --> 00:15:38,104
AND IT'S LESS THAN ONE KILOMETER
FROM OUR SHUTTLEPOD.

254
00:15:38,145 --> 00:15:40,774
TRAVIS: NOT A LOT OF ROOM
ON THAT LANDING PLATFORM.

255
00:15:40,815 --> 00:15:42,442
MAYBE THEY'RE JUST
SOME OTHER VISITORS.

256
00:15:42,483 --> 00:15:45,069
REED: WELL, I FOR ONE WOULD LIKE
TO KNOW WHO THESE VISITORS ARE.

257
00:15:45,111 --> 00:15:47,029
AND WHY HAVEN'T WE HEARD
FROM THE LANDING PARTY?

258
00:15:47,071 --> 00:15:49,949
HOSHI: YOU CAN'T EXPECT THEM
TO CHECK IN EVERY 10 MINUTES.

259
00:15:49,990 --> 00:15:52,786
REED: MAYBE THAT SHOULD BE
STANDARD PROCEDURE, AS WELL.

260
00:15:52,827 --> 00:15:54,328
YOU SURE
YOU'RE NOT OVERREACTING?

261
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:56,122
THEY'RE PROBABLY
JUST TAKING A TOUR,

262
00:15:56,163 --> 00:15:59,125
OBSERVING SOME KIND
OF MEDITATION RITUAL.

263
00:15:59,166 --> 00:16:00,460
[ ARCHER GRUNTS ]

264
00:16:00,501 --> 00:16:03,421
WHERE'S THE SENSOR ARRAY?

265
00:16:03,463 --> 00:16:06,340
FROM WHAT I'M TOLD,
THERE ISN'T ONE.

266
00:16:08,802 --> 00:16:09,844
WHERE IS IT?!

267
00:16:12,513 --> 00:16:13,681
I DON'T KNOW.

268
00:16:17,017 --> 00:16:20,730
YOU HUMANS OBVIOUSLY
HAVE EMOTIONS.

269
00:16:20,772 --> 00:16:23,942
I FIND IT CURIOUS
THAT YOU'D SELECT A VULCAN

270
00:16:23,983 --> 00:16:25,735
AS YOUR SCIENCE OFFICER.

271
00:16:25,777 --> 00:16:29,280
BELIEVE ME,
SHE WASN'T MY FIRST CHOICE.

272
00:16:29,322 --> 00:16:30,323
ALIEN: WHY A VULCAN?

273
00:16:37,413 --> 00:16:38,665
ALIEN: WHY A VULCAN?!

274
00:16:44,462 --> 00:16:48,842
SHE WAS ASSIGNED TO US
BY THE VULCAN HIGH COMMAND.

275
00:16:50,593 --> 00:16:53,304
ALIEN: YOU TAKE ORDERS
FROM THE HIGH COMMAND?

276
00:16:53,346 --> 00:16:56,098
NO.

277
00:16:56,140 --> 00:17:00,645
FOR THE LAST TIME,
WE JUST CAME TO SEE THE TEMPLE.

278
00:17:00,687 --> 00:17:03,606
[ COMMUNICATOR BEEPING ]

279
00:17:03,648 --> 00:17:05,859
ARCHER: THAT'S MY SHIP.

280
00:17:05,900 --> 00:17:08,277
<i>ENTERPRISE.</i>

281
00:17:08,319 --> 00:17:09,737
THEY'RE TRYING TO CONTACT.

282
00:17:09,779 --> 00:17:11,614
UGH!

283
00:17:11,656 --> 00:17:13,700
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

284
00:17:30,257 --> 00:17:31,968
ALIEN:<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

285
00:17:32,010 --> 00:17:34,888
REED: YES, I'M LOOKING
FOR CAPTAIN ARCHER.

286
00:17:34,929 --> 00:17:37,932
ALIEN: HE'S A PRISONER
OF THE ANDORIAN IMPERIAL GUARD.

287
00:17:37,974 --> 00:17:40,935
WE KNOW YOU'RE IN COLLABORATION
WITH THE VULCANS.

288
00:17:40,977 --> 00:17:42,562
LET ME TALK TO THE CAPTAIN.

289
00:17:42,603 --> 00:17:44,939
ALIEN: YOUR SHIP IS UNDER
CONSTANT SURVEILLANCE.

290
00:17:44,981 --> 00:17:46,190
ARM YOUR WEAPONS

291
00:17:46,232 --> 00:17:48,150
OR MAKE ANY ATTEMPT
TO APPROACH THE SURFACE,

292
00:17:48,192 --> 00:17:49,736
AND I'LL KILL THE HOSTAGES.

293
00:17:53,155 --> 00:17:54,114
ARCHER: WAIT!

294
00:17:55,616 --> 00:17:56,826
I'VE LOST THE SIGNAL.

295
00:17:56,868 --> 00:17:59,620
TRY T'POL OR COMMANDER TUCKER.

296
00:18:01,330 --> 00:18:02,456
[ COMMUNICATOR BEEPS ]

297
00:18:05,167 --> 00:18:06,502
[ COMMUNICATOR BEEPS ]

298
00:18:10,798 --> 00:18:12,174
NO RESPONSE.

299
00:18:12,216 --> 00:18:14,301
REED: HAVE LAUNCH BAY PUT
SHUTTLEPOD 2 ON STANDBY.

300
00:18:14,343 --> 00:18:15,302
TRAVIS: YOU HEARD WHAT HE SAID.

301
00:18:15,344 --> 00:18:16,804
IF WE TRY TO SEND
MORE PEOPLE--

302
00:18:16,846 --> 00:18:19,139
REED: I DON'T TAKE ORDERS
FROM A COM VOICE, ENSIGN,

303
00:18:19,181 --> 00:18:21,976
NOT UNLESS THAT VOICE
BELONGS TO THE CAPTAIN.

304
00:18:22,018 --> 00:18:23,603
TAKE A LOOK
AT THE VULCAN DATABASE.

305
00:18:23,644 --> 00:18:25,730
SEE IF IT HAS ANYTHING
ON THESE ANDORIANS.

306
00:18:25,772 --> 00:18:26,773
AYE, SIR.

307
00:18:29,149 --> 00:18:31,527
[ DOOR OPENS ]

308
00:18:31,569 --> 00:18:33,780
ALIEN: WE'VE SEARCHED ALL THE
CHAMBERS IN THE EASTERN TOWER.

309
00:18:33,821 --> 00:18:35,155
ALIEN 2: HAVE YOU CHECKED
THE LIVING QUARTERS?

310
00:18:35,197 --> 00:18:36,198
ALIEN: NOT YET.

311
00:18:42,496 --> 00:18:46,000
ALIEN: PERHAPS IF WE DECAPITATE
ONE OR TWO OF THOSE MONKS,

312
00:18:46,042 --> 00:18:47,543
HE'LL START TELLING US
THE TRUTH.

313
00:18:53,967 --> 00:19:00,765
ALIEN 2: IS THAT SOMETHING
YOU COULD LIVE WITH, CAPTAIN?

314
00:19:00,807 --> 00:19:03,017
ARCHER: I'VE ALREADY
TOLD YOU THE TRUTH.

315
00:19:12,652 --> 00:19:15,613
ELDER: HOW LONG HAVE YOU LIVED
ON THE EARTH SHIP?

316
00:19:15,655 --> 00:19:19,659
T'POL: 9 WEEKS AND 4 DAYS.

317
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:21,911
ELDER: THE SMELL MUST
BE INTOLERABLE.

318
00:19:21,953 --> 00:19:24,122
T'POL: YOU GET USED TO IT.

319
00:19:24,163 --> 00:19:26,749
AND I WAS GIVEN
A NASAL NUMBING AGENT.

320
00:19:26,791 --> 00:19:27,959
[ DOOR OPENS ]

321
00:19:37,885 --> 00:19:40,220
ARCHER: WHOSE IDEA WAS IT
TO VISIT THIS PLACE?

322
00:19:40,262 --> 00:19:41,305
[ GROANS ]

323
00:19:44,058 --> 00:19:46,644
THESE GUYS ARE SERIOUS.

324
00:19:46,686 --> 00:19:50,148
[ PANTING ]

325
00:19:50,230 --> 00:19:51,565
THEY'RE GONNA START
KILLING YOU PEOPLE

326
00:19:51,607 --> 00:19:54,193
IF THEY DON'T FIND
WHAT THEY'RE LOOKING FOR.

327
00:19:54,234 --> 00:19:56,320
ELDER: THERE IS
NOTHING TO FIND.

328
00:19:56,362 --> 00:19:59,532
ARCHER: I DON'T THINK
THEY'RE BUYING THAT.

329
00:19:59,573 --> 00:20:00,533
NOT THIS TIME.

330
00:20:03,703 --> 00:20:06,497
LOOKS LIKE THERE
ARE 4 OF THEM.

331
00:20:06,539 --> 00:20:08,290
I SAW SOME KIND
OF SCANNING CONSOLE.

332
00:20:11,418 --> 00:20:13,212
THEY TALKED A LOT
ABOUT SEARCHING ROOMS.

333
00:20:15,297 --> 00:20:17,299
TUCKER: YOU'D THINK THEY COULD
FIND WHATEVER IT IS
THEY'RE LOOKING FOR

334
00:20:17,341 --> 00:20:18,718
WITH THOSE ANTENNAS OF THEIRS.

335
00:20:20,469 --> 00:20:24,015
THEY ANSWERED A HAIL
FROM<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

336
00:20:24,057 --> 00:20:26,684
THEY THREATENED TO KILL US ALL
IF ANYONE ATTEMPTS A RESCUE.

337
00:20:26,726 --> 00:20:28,978
T'POL: MR. REED WOULDN'T
BE THAT RECKLESS.

338
00:20:29,020 --> 00:20:30,312
I DIDN'T RECRUIT
MY TACTICAL OFFICER

339
00:20:30,354 --> 00:20:32,314
TO SIT ON HIS BUTT
WHEN HE'S THREATENED.

340
00:20:35,317 --> 00:20:37,444
THE ANDORIANS SMASHED
OUR COMMUNICATORS.

341
00:20:40,156 --> 00:20:43,159
THE LONGER WE'RE
OUT OF CONTACT,

342
00:20:43,201 --> 00:20:46,162
THE MORE LIKELY
MALCOLM WILL PUT TOGETHER

343
00:20:46,204 --> 00:20:51,918
A LANDING PARTY,
WARNING OR NO WARNING.

344
00:20:51,959 --> 00:20:54,754
TUCKER: KNOWING HIM,
A HEAVILY ARMED LANDING PARTY.

345
00:20:54,795 --> 00:20:57,840
ARCHER: IT'S JUST
A MATTER OF TIME.

346
00:20:57,882 --> 00:21:02,261
SO IF ANYONE HAS A SUGGESTION,
I'M ALL EARS.

347
00:21:04,764 --> 00:21:05,765
NO OFFENSE.

348
00:21:08,517 --> 00:21:10,144
ELDER: THERE IS AN OPTION.

349
00:21:10,186 --> 00:21:12,772
A TRANSMITTER--IT'S VERY OLD.

350
00:21:12,813 --> 00:21:15,357
YOU SAID YOU HAD NO TECHNOLOGY.

351
00:21:15,399 --> 00:21:17,110
ELDER: IT HASN'T BEEN USED
IN MANY YEARS.

352
00:21:17,151 --> 00:21:18,694
IT MAY NOT EVEN BE WORKING.

353
00:21:18,736 --> 00:21:21,488
TUCKER: I NEVER MET A
BUSTED RADIO I COULDN'T FIX.

354
00:21:21,530 --> 00:21:24,408
WHERE IS THIS TRANSMITTER?

355
00:21:27,161 --> 00:21:28,579
VULCAN: IN THE CATACOMBS.

356
00:21:31,249 --> 00:21:32,250
TUCKER: CATACOMBS?

357
00:21:33,876 --> 00:21:36,170
ELDER: PLEASE LISTEN
TO ME, CAPTAIN.

358
00:21:36,212 --> 00:21:38,714
THERE ARE HIDDEN PASSAGES
BENEATH US

359
00:21:38,756 --> 00:21:41,259
WHERE WE KEEP OUR
MOST SACRED RELICS--

360
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:42,384
OUR HONORED DEAD.

361
00:21:47,389 --> 00:21:50,392
IF THE ANDORIANS DISCOVER THEM,
THEY WILL DAMAGE OUR CULTURE

362
00:21:50,434 --> 00:21:52,519
IN WAYS YOU CAN'T
BEGIN TO UNDERSTAND.

363
00:21:59,277 --> 00:22:00,444
TUCKER: FOR PEOPLE
WITHOUT EMOTION,

364
00:22:00,486 --> 00:22:02,321
YOU SURE HAVE A FLAIR
FOR THE DRAMATIC.

365
00:23:13,726 --> 00:23:15,769
[ GASPS ]

366
00:23:15,811 --> 00:23:19,690
MASTER HAADOK,
ONE OF THE FOUNDERS OF P'JEM.

367
00:23:21,025 --> 00:23:23,277
THE TRANSMITTER'S THIS WAY.

368
00:23:27,907 --> 00:23:28,908
FELLAS.

369
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:56,394
WHAT'S DOWN THERE?

370
00:23:56,434 --> 00:23:57,937
VULCAN: THE RELIQUARY.

371
00:23:57,978 --> 00:23:59,980
OUR MOST SACRED ARTIFACTS
ARE KEPT THERE.

372
00:24:00,022 --> 00:24:01,648
THIS IS THE TRANSMITTER.

373
00:24:20,376 --> 00:24:22,002
LOOKS LIKE
A KRELLIDE POWER CELL.

374
00:25:03,585 --> 00:25:05,045
ELDER: THERE IS ONE TO SPARE.

375
00:25:05,087 --> 00:25:06,713
TUCKER: NO, THANKS.
IT'LL JUST GET IN MY WAY.

376
00:25:10,468 --> 00:25:12,345
ELDER: IT'S ONLY GOING
TO GET COLDER.

377
00:25:15,681 --> 00:25:17,391
ARCHER: YOU TAKE IT.

378
00:25:17,433 --> 00:25:18,725
T'POL: YOU NEED IT
MORE THAN I DO.

379
00:25:29,362 --> 00:25:31,697
ARCHER: DO THE ANDORIANS
HAVE A TRANSPORTER?

380
00:25:31,738 --> 00:25:33,699
T'POL: NO.

381
00:25:33,740 --> 00:25:35,742
ARCHER: THAT GIVES US
THE ELEMENT OF SURPRISE.

382
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:40,331
WE COULD BRING AN ASSAULT
TEAM RIGHT INTO THE ATRIUM.

383
00:25:40,373 --> 00:25:43,167
T'POL: THE SOUND OF
THE TRANSPORTER ALONE
WOULD ALERT THE GUARDS.

384
00:25:43,209 --> 00:25:47,087
THEY'D START FIRING BEFORE
THE TEAM WAS FULLY RESEQUENCED.

385
00:25:47,129 --> 00:25:49,507
WELL, WHAT ABOUT THIS ROOM?

386
00:25:49,547 --> 00:25:52,051
BY THE TIME THE ANDORIANS
DETECTED THE TRANSPORT,

387
00:25:52,092 --> 00:25:53,135
WE'D BE ARMED AND READY.

388
00:25:53,177 --> 00:25:54,928
T'POL: FOR WHAT?

389
00:25:54,970 --> 00:25:59,308
A FIREFIGHT IN CLOSE QUARTERS,
WITH A DOZEN MONKS AT RISK?

390
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:01,310
IF YOU'VE GOT
ANY BETTER IDEAS...

391
00:26:09,485 --> 00:26:11,569
THERE'S ROOM IN HERE.

392
00:26:11,611 --> 00:26:12,779
T'POL: I'M FINE.

393
00:26:12,821 --> 00:26:14,572
YOU'RE FREEZING.

394
00:26:14,614 --> 00:26:15,699
IT'S BEEN 24 HOURS

395
00:26:15,741 --> 00:26:18,911
SINCE I TOOK
MY NASAL NUMBING AGENT.

396
00:26:18,952 --> 00:26:21,663
THE COLD IS PREFERABLE
TO THE ODOR.

397
00:26:21,705 --> 00:26:22,831
COME ON.

398
00:26:42,059 --> 00:26:44,937
T'POL: AN ARMED ASSAULT WOULD
PUT ALL OF OUR LIVES AT RISK,

399
00:26:44,978 --> 00:26:48,857
NOT TO MENTION THE DESTRUCTION
OF THE SANCTUARY ITSELF.

400
00:26:48,899 --> 00:26:51,902
ARCHER: I'D SAY OUR LIVES
ARE ALREADY AT RISK.

401
00:26:51,944 --> 00:26:56,073
T'POL: TENSIONS BETWEEN ANDORIA
AND VULCAN ARE HIGH.

402
00:26:56,115 --> 00:26:58,616
ANY CASUALTIES WOULD
ONLY MAKE MATTERS WORSE.

403
00:27:01,495 --> 00:27:04,748
ARCHER: IT SEEMS LIKE YOU'RE
LETTING THEM WALK ALL OVER YOU.

404
00:27:04,790 --> 00:27:06,125
THEY COME IN HERE,
THEY SMASH YOUR RELICS,

405
00:27:06,166 --> 00:27:07,918
THEY BEAT UP YOUR PEOPLE.

406
00:27:07,960 --> 00:27:10,296
THEN YOU JUST SIT BACK AND
WAIT FOR THEM TO WALK AWAY?

407
00:27:10,337 --> 00:27:11,589
T'POL: WE DON'T BELIEVE

408
00:27:11,629 --> 00:27:15,342
IN RESPONDING
TO VIOLENCE WITH VIOLENCE.

409
00:27:15,384 --> 00:27:17,803
ARCHER: I ADMIRE YOUR ETHICS,

410
00:27:17,844 --> 00:27:21,557
BUT RIGHT NOW,
A LITTLE VIOLENCE MIGHT HELP.

411
00:27:21,599 --> 00:27:24,977
T'POL: YOU'RE BEGINNING
TO SOUND LIKE AN ANDORIAN.

412
00:27:25,018 --> 00:27:26,145
ARCHER: YOU KNOW, I CAME HERE

413
00:27:26,186 --> 00:27:27,229
HOPING TO GAIN A LITTLE INSIGHT

414
00:27:27,271 --> 00:27:28,939
INTO THE VULCAN MIND.

415
00:27:28,981 --> 00:27:30,690
IT LOOKS LIKE I'M GETTING IT.

416
00:27:30,732 --> 00:27:33,611
YOU PEOPLE THINK YOU'RE
SO DAMNED ENLIGHTENED.

417
00:27:33,651 --> 00:27:34,652
PROBLEM?

418
00:27:44,121 --> 00:27:48,334
I'D LIKE TO FIND
A PEACEFUL SOLUTION, TOO,

419
00:27:48,375 --> 00:27:49,876
BUT I DON'T THINK
THAT'S GONNA HAPPEN.

420
00:27:53,922 --> 00:27:56,342
HOWEVER WE END UP
DEALING WITH THIS,

421
00:27:56,383 --> 00:27:58,760
I NEED TO KNOW I
CAN COUNT ON YOU.

422
00:27:58,802 --> 00:28:01,514
T'POL: ARE YOU QUESTIONING
MY LOYALTY?

423
00:28:01,555 --> 00:28:04,724
ARCHER: I JUST WANT TO KNOW
WHERE WE STAND.

424
00:28:04,766 --> 00:28:08,145
T'POL: I HAVE NEVER
DISOBEYED YOUR ORDERS.

425
00:28:27,331 --> 00:28:29,625
TRAVIS: SIR, YOU'RE WEARING
A HOLE IN THE DECK PLATING.

426
00:28:29,667 --> 00:28:30,876
[ COMPUTER BEEPING ]

427
00:28:30,917 --> 00:28:32,169
REED: WHAT IS IT?

428
00:28:32,211 --> 00:28:33,753
TRANSMISSION FROM THE SURFACE.

429
00:28:33,795 --> 00:28:36,590
IT'S A MODULATED E.M. SIGNAL,
VERY WEAK.

430
00:28:36,632 --> 00:28:37,633
REED: PUT IT THROUGH.

431
00:28:39,218 --> 00:28:42,179
TUCKER:<i> ENTERPRISE,</i> 
THIS IS COMMANDER TUCKER.

432
00:28:42,221 --> 00:28:45,474
REPEAT--<i> ENTERPRISE,</i> 
THIS IS COMMANDER TUCKER.

433
00:28:45,516 --> 00:28:47,851
THIS IS<i> ENTERPRISE.</i> WE CAN
BARELY READ YOU, COMMANDER.

434
00:28:47,893 --> 00:28:49,645
WHAT'S YOUR STATUS?

435
00:28:49,687 --> 00:28:52,939
TUCKER: GUESS YOU HEARD.
WE KIND OF WALKED INTO
A HOSTAGE SITUATION.

436
00:28:52,981 --> 00:28:54,858
THE WHOLE PLACE HAS BEEN
TAKEN OVER BY ANDORIANS.

437
00:28:54,900 --> 00:28:56,318
REED: ANDORIANS, YES.

438
00:28:56,360 --> 00:28:59,071
I'VE BEEN READING ABOUT THEM
IN THE VULCAN DATABASE.

439
00:28:59,112 --> 00:29:00,531
MILITARISTIC, BLUE-SKINNED?

440
00:29:00,573 --> 00:29:01,532
TUCKER: THAT'S THEM.

441
00:29:01,574 --> 00:29:03,283
REED: WELL, WHAT DO THEY WANT?

442
00:29:03,325 --> 00:29:04,451
TUCKER: THEY SEEM
TO THINK THIS PLACE IS

443
00:29:04,493 --> 00:29:06,995
SOME KIND OF A SPY STATION.

444
00:29:07,037 --> 00:29:08,997
THEY'RE LOOKING
FOR A SENSOR ARRAY.

445
00:29:09,039 --> 00:29:10,708
THE CAPTAIN SAYS TO SIT TIGHT.

446
00:29:10,749 --> 00:29:13,669
HE DOESN'T WANT TO PROVOKE THEM
ANY MORE THAN WE ALREADY HAVE.

447
00:29:13,711 --> 00:29:15,462
HE ALSO SAID TO TELL YOU

448
00:29:15,504 --> 00:29:17,214
WE'RE WORKING ON A WAY
OUT OF HERE.

449
00:29:17,256 --> 00:29:19,216
ARE YOU CERTAIN
WE CAN'T NEGOTIATE?

450
00:29:19,258 --> 00:29:21,176
THE CAPTAIN CAME BACK
FROM HIS LAST NEGOTIATION

451
00:29:21,218 --> 00:29:23,512
WITH A FACE FULL OF BRUISES.

452
00:29:23,554 --> 00:29:24,804
TUCKER: WE'LL BE IN TOUCH.

453
00:29:24,846 --> 00:29:25,847
UNDERSTOOD.

454
00:29:33,772 --> 00:29:36,650
ARCHER: DO ANY OF THESE TUNNELS
LEAD TO THE OUTSIDE?

455
00:29:36,692 --> 00:29:39,445
ELDER: NO.

456
00:29:39,486 --> 00:29:42,364
ARCHER: WHAT ABOUT
THIS RELIQUARY?

457
00:29:42,406 --> 00:29:44,074
VULCAN: NO ONE'S
ENTERED IT IN YEARS.

458
00:29:44,116 --> 00:29:46,368
ELDER: TO DO SO
WOULD BE BLASPHEMY.

459
00:29:46,410 --> 00:29:48,746
TUCKER: I SAW AN OLD STAIRWELL
DOWN THERE,

460
00:29:48,787 --> 00:29:49,705
MAYBE A METER WIDE.

461
00:29:49,747 --> 00:29:53,083
IT WAS RIGHT ABOUT HERE.

462
00:29:53,125 --> 00:29:56,044
T'POL: THAT WOULD ALMOST BE
DIRECTLY BENEATH THE ATRIUM.

463
00:29:56,086 --> 00:29:58,171
TUCKER: THERE WERE 3 DIM LIGHTS
COMING FROM THE TOP.

464
00:29:58,213 --> 00:30:00,840
IT LOOKED SOMETHING LIKE THIS.

465
00:30:07,681 --> 00:30:10,350
ALIEN: HOW MANY TIMES DO WE
HAVE TO SEARCH THE SAME ROOMS?

466
00:30:10,392 --> 00:30:11,602
ALIEN 2: ARE YOU LOSING FAITH
IN OUR MISSION?

467
00:30:11,644 --> 00:30:12,561
ALIEN: WE'VE LOOKED EVERYWHERE.

468
00:30:12,603 --> 00:30:14,772
WE'VE RUN A THOUSAND SCANS!

469
00:30:18,150 --> 00:30:22,154
ALIEN 2: THE VULCANS
ARE VERY DECEPTIVE.

470
00:30:24,531 --> 00:30:29,328
IT'S HERE. I'M SURE OF IT.

471
00:30:29,369 --> 00:30:30,912
IF WE BACK DOWN NOW,

472
00:30:30,954 --> 00:30:34,667
EVERYTHING WE'VE FOUGHT FOR
IS MEANINGLESS!

473
00:30:34,708 --> 00:30:37,503
IF NOTHING ELSE,
REMEMBER THAT, KEVAL.

474
00:30:37,544 --> 00:30:39,254
TUCKER: HEY!

475
00:30:39,296 --> 00:30:40,964
CAN YOU HEAR ME?

476
00:30:41,006 --> 00:30:43,175
HELLO?

477
00:30:43,216 --> 00:30:44,217
ANYBODY OUT THERE?

478
00:30:55,437 --> 00:30:58,398
ARCHER: I NEED TO SPEAK
WITH YOU ALONE.

479
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,858
I HAVE SOME INFORMATION
FOR YOU.

480
00:31:12,538 --> 00:31:14,414
ALIEN: WHAT IS IT?

481
00:31:14,456 --> 00:31:19,294
ARCHER: WELL, FOR ONE THING,
I NEEDED SOME FRESH AIR.

482
00:31:19,336 --> 00:31:21,129
YOU EVER BEEN STUCK IN A ROOM
FULL OF VULCANS FOR 12 HOURS?

483
00:31:21,171 --> 00:31:22,548
ALIEN: THE INFORMATION.

484
00:31:22,589 --> 00:31:24,090
ARCHER: I'LL BET THEIR ROBES
HAVEN'T BEEN WASHED

485
00:31:24,132 --> 00:31:26,009
SINCE THE TIME OF SURAK.

486
00:31:26,051 --> 00:31:26,968
HAVE YOU HEARD OF HIM?

487
00:31:27,010 --> 00:31:28,679
VULCAN PHILOSOPHER.

488
00:31:28,721 --> 00:31:33,016
HE'S THE ONE WHO GOT EVERYBODY
TO START PURGING THEIR EMOTIONS.

489
00:31:33,058 --> 00:31:34,685
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU,
BUT I HAVE LEARNED

490
00:31:34,727 --> 00:31:36,854
REALLY A LOT SINCE I GOT HERE.

491
00:31:36,895 --> 00:31:37,896
[ GROANING ]

492
00:31:41,983 --> 00:31:44,944
ALIEN: WHAT DID YOU
COME TO TELL US?

493
00:31:44,986 --> 00:31:47,280
ARCHER: WELL, THAT DEPENDS.

494
00:31:47,322 --> 00:31:49,783
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO KNOW?

495
00:31:49,825 --> 00:31:50,826
OH!

496
00:31:54,246 --> 00:31:55,539
ALL RIGHT.

497
00:31:55,581 --> 00:31:56,707
INFORMATION.

498
00:31:58,458 --> 00:32:00,544
DID YOU KNOW THAT...

499
00:32:00,586 --> 00:32:05,131
OVER 70% OF THE ORGANISMS
ON MY HOMEWORLD ARE BACTERIA?

500
00:32:05,173 --> 00:32:06,592
WHAT?

501
00:32:06,633 --> 00:32:09,928
HERE'S SOMETHING
I THINK YOU'LL FIND INTERESTING.

502
00:32:09,969 --> 00:32:12,765
THERE WAS A MAN IN CANTON, OHIO,
WHO ONCE ROLLED

503
00:32:12,806 --> 00:32:17,227
A BALL OF STRING
OVER 6 METERS IN DIAMETER.

504
00:32:17,269 --> 00:32:19,145
[ GROANING ]

505
00:32:19,187 --> 00:32:21,565
HE'S WASTING OUR TIME.
TAKE HIM BACK!

506
00:32:21,607 --> 00:32:24,150
THERE WAS A FAMOUS ASTRONOMER
ON EARTH...

507
00:32:27,237 --> 00:32:29,364
TYCHO BRAHE.

508
00:32:29,406 --> 00:32:32,242
HE LOST HIS NOSE IN A DUEL...

509
00:32:32,284 --> 00:32:33,493
[ LAUGHS ]

510
00:32:33,535 --> 00:32:35,662
...OVER A MATH EQUATION!

511
00:32:35,704 --> 00:32:36,705
UGH!

512
00:32:37,664 --> 00:32:38,957
ALIEN: YOU MUST ENJOY PAIN.

513
00:32:40,793 --> 00:32:42,252
ARCHER: PLEASE.

514
00:32:42,294 --> 00:32:46,005
PLEASE, I CAN'T STAND ANOTHER
MINUTE WITH THE VULCANS!

515
00:32:46,047 --> 00:32:47,006
PLEASE!

516
00:33:13,951 --> 00:33:15,994
[ ARCHER GROANING ]

517
00:33:29,257 --> 00:33:30,425
A LIGHT AT THE END
OF THE TUNNEL.

518
00:33:32,385 --> 00:33:33,553
YOU KNOW WHAT TO DO, COMMANDER.

519
00:33:33,595 --> 00:33:35,221
YES, SIR.

520
00:33:35,263 --> 00:33:37,182
ELDER: I DON'T HAVE
TO TELL YOU, CAPTAIN,

521
00:33:37,223 --> 00:33:39,643
WE DON'T CONDONE THESE ACTIONS
YOU ARE ABOUT TO TAKE.

522
00:33:39,685 --> 00:33:42,980
ARCHER: NO, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO TELL ME.

523
00:33:43,021 --> 00:33:44,189
JUST TRY AND STAY
OUT OF THE WAY,

524
00:33:44,230 --> 00:33:45,691
AND EVERYTHING WILL
WORK OUT FINE.

525
00:33:49,277 --> 00:33:51,321
REED: PHASE PISTOLS ON STUN.
CREWMAN: STUN, SIR?

526
00:33:51,363 --> 00:33:53,114
REED: THE CAPTAIN'S INSTRUCTIONS
WERE QUITE EXPLICIT.

527
00:33:56,952 --> 00:33:59,204
REED: IT'S A CONSOLE, ENSIGN.
IT WON'T BITE.

528
00:33:59,245 --> 00:34:01,456
HOSHI: NO, IT'LL JUST
SCRAMBLE YOUR MOLECULES.

529
00:34:03,249 --> 00:34:04,459
REED: CREWMAN?

530
00:34:04,501 --> 00:34:06,670
CREWMAN: WE'VE, UH...
HEARD STORIES, SIR.

531
00:34:06,712 --> 00:34:07,796
IT MIGHT NOT BE SAFE.

532
00:34:07,838 --> 00:34:09,923
REED: I'VE HEARD
THE SAME STORIES.

533
00:34:09,965 --> 00:34:11,132
NOW GET UP HERE.

534
00:34:13,301 --> 00:34:14,678
COORDINATES SET?

535
00:34:14,720 --> 00:34:16,221
HOSHI: AYE, SIR.

536
00:34:16,262 --> 00:34:19,391
REED: THEN ENERGIZE...
BEFORE WE CHANGE OUR MINDS.

537
00:34:29,108 --> 00:34:31,361
[ ALARM BEEPING ]

538
00:34:31,403 --> 00:34:32,571
ALIEN: WHAT IS IT?

539
00:34:32,612 --> 00:34:34,447
ALIEN 2: SOME KIND OF
ENERGY FLUCTUATION.

540
00:34:45,291 --> 00:34:47,878
ALIEN: WE DETECTED
AN ENERGY SURGE.

541
00:34:47,920 --> 00:34:49,713
IT CAME FROM THIS CHAMBER.

542
00:34:49,755 --> 00:34:52,674
T'POL: PERHAPS YOU HAVE
FAULTY EQUIPMENT.

543
00:34:52,716 --> 00:34:55,594
ALIEN: OR PERHAPS YOU HAVE
EQUIPMENT WE DON'T KNOW ABOUT.

544
00:35:02,059 --> 00:35:03,101
WATCH THEM.

545
00:35:19,451 --> 00:35:20,493
REED: THIS IS IT.

546
00:35:29,252 --> 00:35:31,630
ALIEN: MOST VULCANS
SMELL OF DUST.

547
00:35:34,633 --> 00:35:36,217
BUT YOU'RE DIFFERENT.

548
00:35:36,259 --> 00:35:37,844
TUCKER:<i> SOMETHING</i> SURE SMELLS.

549
00:35:37,886 --> 00:35:39,638
DID YOU SAY SOMETHING,
PINK-SKIN?!

550
00:35:59,950 --> 00:36:01,827
KEVAL: THIS CAN'T BE RIGHT.

551
00:36:01,868 --> 00:36:04,913
I'M DETECTING
3 NEW BIO-SIGNS,

552
00:36:04,955 --> 00:36:06,247
ALL HUMAN.

553
00:36:06,289 --> 00:36:07,499
ALIEN: WHERE ARE THEY?

554
00:36:07,540 --> 00:36:09,417
KEVAL: THEY'RE
WITHIN 20 METERS.

555
00:36:09,459 --> 00:36:10,543
ALIEN: WHERE?!

556
00:36:10,585 --> 00:36:13,088
KEVAL: I CAN'T
PINPOINT THE SIGNAL.

557
00:36:13,130 --> 00:36:14,965
ALIEN: TRY BOOSTING
THE PROXIMITY SENSORS.

558
00:36:20,345 --> 00:36:23,974
ALIEN: I'VE HEARD ABOUT
YOUR MATING RITUALS...

559
00:36:24,016 --> 00:36:26,184
THAT VULCAN WOMEN
FORCE THEIR MEN

560
00:36:26,225 --> 00:36:28,145
TO FIGHT EACH OTHER
TO THE DEATH.

561
00:36:30,689 --> 00:36:32,899
WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO KILL SOMEONE FOR YOU?

562
00:36:37,278 --> 00:36:38,363
ARCHER: LEAVE HER ALONE.

563
00:36:43,660 --> 00:36:45,244
ALIEN: WOULD YOU LIKE ME
TO KILL<i> HIM?</i>

564
00:36:52,794 --> 00:36:54,671
ALIEN: FIND THEM!

565
00:36:54,713 --> 00:36:56,339
KEVAL: THEY'RE VERY CLOSE.

566
00:36:56,381 --> 00:36:58,383
[ ALARM BEEPING ]

567
00:37:02,679 --> 00:37:04,681
[ TUCKER GRUNTING ]

568
00:37:17,903 --> 00:37:19,196
REED: WILL YOU BE ALL RIGHT?

569
00:37:19,237 --> 00:37:21,031
CREWMAN: GO AHEAD.
I'LL COVER HERE.

570
00:37:21,073 --> 00:37:22,074
KEVAL!

571
00:37:32,834 --> 00:37:33,919
REED: THIS WAY.

572
00:37:35,628 --> 00:37:37,630
[ ALIEN GRUNTING ]

573
00:37:44,596 --> 00:37:46,014
UGH!

574
00:37:51,186 --> 00:37:52,229
REED: TWO OF THEM GOT AWAY.

575
00:37:52,270 --> 00:37:53,312
THEY WENT DOWN
INTO THE CATACOMBS.

576
00:37:53,354 --> 00:37:54,773
I HOPE YOU'RE PLEASED, CAPTAIN.

577
00:37:54,814 --> 00:37:57,734
YOU'VE TURNED A PLACE
OF SOLITUDE INTO A WAR ZONE.

578
00:37:57,776 --> 00:37:59,402
ARCHER: WHERE ARE
THE PHASE PISTOLS?
REED: HERE, SIR.

579
00:38:04,574 --> 00:38:06,910
ARCHER: IF HE WAKES UP,
STUN HIM AGAIN.

580
00:38:11,581 --> 00:38:13,458
LET'S GO.

581
00:38:13,499 --> 00:38:14,918
VULCAN: I'M GOING WITH YOU.

582
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:17,503
ELDER: VIOLENCE IS
NO LONGER OUR WAY.

583
00:38:17,545 --> 00:38:19,172
WE MUST PROTECT WHAT IS OURS.

584
00:38:37,816 --> 00:38:40,359
THEY'RE DOWN THIS PASSAGE.
30 METERS.

585
00:38:41,778 --> 00:38:43,280
VULCAN: IT LEADS
TO THE RELIQUARY.

586
00:38:43,321 --> 00:38:45,282
ONLY MEMBERS OF THE HIGH ORDER
ARE ALLOWED TO GO INSIDE.

587
00:38:45,323 --> 00:38:46,449
ARCHER: WE'LL DO OUR BEST
NOT TO LOOK AT ANYTHING.

588
00:38:46,491 --> 00:38:48,534
VULCAN: I CAN'T
PERMIT IT, CAPTAIN.

589
00:38:48,576 --> 00:38:50,495
ARCHER: WHAT WOULD
YOU SUGGEST WE DO?

590
00:38:50,536 --> 00:38:52,164
VULCAN: I'LL
DISARM THEM MYSELF.

591
00:38:52,205 --> 00:38:53,372
ARCHER: YOU EVER
USE ONE OF THOSE?

592
00:38:55,041 --> 00:38:56,501
I DIDN'T THINK SO.

593
00:38:56,542 --> 00:38:57,961
THE ANDORIANS HAVE SEEN
YOUR SACRED RELICS.

594
00:38:58,003 --> 00:38:59,545
A COUPLE HUMANS WON'T MAKE
MUCH OF A DIFFERENCE.

595
00:39:43,589 --> 00:39:44,549
CAPTAIN.

596
00:40:18,291 --> 00:40:19,417
HOLD YOUR FIRE!

597
00:40:21,002 --> 00:40:22,712
YOU MIGHT WANT TO TAKE
A LOOK AT THIS!

598
00:40:51,574 --> 00:40:53,076
ARCHER: I DON'T BELIEVE THIS.

599
00:41:05,504 --> 00:41:08,341
ARCHER: DOES THAT THING
HAVE IMAGING SENSORS?

600
00:41:08,383 --> 00:41:10,802
T'POL: YES.

601
00:41:10,843 --> 00:41:12,678
TAKE ALL THE PICTURES YOU CAN.

602
00:41:15,140 --> 00:41:17,100
VULCAN: PLACE YOUR WEAPONS
ON THE GROUND.

603
00:41:17,142 --> 00:41:20,812
I...WILL KILL HIM IF NECESSARY.

604
00:41:25,650 --> 00:41:26,734
GIVE THAT TO ME.

605
00:41:29,112 --> 00:41:30,155
ARCHER: UGH!

606
00:41:34,451 --> 00:41:36,369
REED: VIOLENCE IN
A SANCTUARY, CAPTAIN?

607
00:41:36,411 --> 00:41:39,956
ARCHER: VERY DISRESPECTFUL,
BUT, BOY, DID IT FEEL GOOD.

608
00:41:42,417 --> 00:41:47,422
ALL THIS TIME, THEY'VE BEEN
CALLING THESE MONKS LIARS,

609
00:41:47,464 --> 00:41:49,882
AND ALL THIS TIME
THEY'VE BEEN RIGHT.

610
00:41:49,924 --> 00:41:51,592
REED: THEY'VE GOT ENOUGH
EQUIPMENT DOWN THERE TO SEE

611
00:41:51,634 --> 00:41:53,719
WHAT ANY ANDORIAN IS
HAVING FOR BREAKFAST.

612
00:41:55,596 --> 00:41:57,765
T'POL: I'VE COMPLETED MY SCANS.

613
00:41:57,807 --> 00:41:59,976
ARCHER: GIVE IT TO HIM.
T'POL: SIR?

614
00:42:00,018 --> 00:42:00,977
ARCHER: GIVE IT TO HIM.

615
00:42:09,735 --> 00:42:11,529
YOU GOT WHAT YOU CAME FOR.
NOW GET OUT OF HERE.

616
00:42:13,281 --> 00:42:15,367
HOW DO WE KNOW YOU
WON'T ATTACK OUR VESSEL?

617
00:42:15,408 --> 00:42:17,118
THE VULCANS VIOLATED
YOUR TREATY.

618
00:42:17,160 --> 00:42:18,661
YOUR PEOPLE
OUGHT TO KNOW ABOUT IT.

619
00:42:20,079 --> 00:42:21,539
ARCHER: YOU HAVE
A PROBLEM WITH THAT?

620
00:42:25,043 --> 00:42:26,169
YOUR COMMUNICATOR.

621
00:42:33,051 --> 00:42:34,469
T'POL TO<i> ENTERPRISE.</i>

622
00:42:34,511 --> 00:42:35,428
TRAVIS: GO AHEAD.

623
00:42:35,470 --> 00:42:36,595
THE ANDORIAN SHIP

624
00:42:36,637 --> 00:42:38,515
WILL BE LEAVING THE SURFACE
MOMENTARILY.

625
00:42:40,892 --> 00:42:42,185
T'POL: THEY'RE FREE TO GO.

626
00:42:42,227 --> 00:42:43,228
TRAVIS: ACKNOWLEDGED.

627
00:42:55,281 --> 00:42:56,533
ALIEN: WE'RE IN YOUR DEBT.

628
00:43:08,127 --> 00:43:09,295
THANKS FOR THE TOUR.
